sections.heading: of Nebraska; establishment; name
sections.text: There has been established and shall be maintained in this state an institution under the name and style of the University of Nebraska.SourceLaws 1869, § 1, p. 172;R.S.1913, § 7081;C.S.1922, § 6713;C.S.1929, § 85-101;R.S.1943, § 85-101.AnnotationsUniversity of Nebras
